languages.text: “我知道死者之前是做什么的，我也很清楚你在他手下扮演着什么样的角色。”

languages.text: «Dada la anterior ocupación del fallecido, puedo imaginar qué función desempeñaba bajo su mando».
languages.original_text: "Given the deceased's former occupation, I have a good idea what role you played under his command."

languages.text: 「亡くなった者の前職から察するに、お前が奴の指揮下でどのような役割を担っていたのか推測できる」
languages.original_text: "Given the deceased's former occupation, I have a good idea what role you played under his command."

languages.text: "In Anbetracht des früheren Berufs des Verstorbenen kann ich mir gut vorstellen, welche Rolle Ihr unter seinem Kommando gespielt habt."
languages.original_text: "Given the deceased's former occupation, I have a good idea what role you played under his command."

languages.text: « Vu les activités passées du défunt, je pense pouvoir deviner quelle fonction vous occupiez sous son commandement. »

languages.text: "Rahmetlinin eski mesleğini düşününce, emri altında nasıl bir görev üstlendiğini tahmin edebiliyorum."
languages.original_text: "Given the deceased's former occupation, I have a good idea what role you played under his command."
